      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Also, I think it would be a good idea that if a `depends/${host}/share/config.site` file exists, bitcoin `configure` script would just use `depends/$(host)` as the default `--prefix` value instead of `/usr/local`.\r\n\r\nThis way using depends would just require running 'make -C depends; ./configure; make` without needing to figure out the host triple or look at depends output.",
